parameters:
Whoa! What's up? Being approached while I'm enjoying myself
with this girl... it's tough being a popular guy, huh\I[15]

I'm just happy being with you... I'm asking for a lap pillow
until dawn

Shall we eat unaju together? After all, our bodies are our
assets in this line of work. Make sure to get plenty of
nutrition.

It's good that the fire earlier was just a small one, huh?
But Shouemon-san was pale as a ghost; did something happen?

Momiji-san, it's been over 20 years since you came to this
brothel, and yet you haven't changed at all... Perhaps
you're something like a zashiki-warashi. Just kidding, haha.

Hey! Are you a courtesan like me? Don't butt in while I'm
working. Hmph!

My husband ran off in the night because of his debts... I've
got no choice but to make a living here. It takes a lot of
physical and mental strength, but you can earn a decent
amount. You should work hard too.

Momiji-san also works as a bodyguard for the pleasure
district. Just the other day, she took down a violent
samurai with a single blow. Amazing, isn't it?

They say there's a door in this pleasure district that never
opens. Beyond it lies the burnt remains of the old red-light
district, or so the story goes.

The inner chamber is a "Forbidden Room," and entry is
prohibited. I've informed the other courtesans as well. You
must absolutely not enter, okay?

The gate ahead actually leads to a passage to the old red-
light district. It's been off-limits because ghosts have
been known to appear. If you're going, be careful...

I try to remember the faces of the clients who come and go
in the red-light district, but it's hard to match them with
the one who disappeared... Perhaps the culprit is in
disguise. For the sake of protecting the courtesans, please
find the perpetrator quickly.

Good grief, to think that an oni had come to this brothel as
a customer... If the other clients find out, it'll be a
major issue. Could you take care of the oni discreetly?

Thanks to Karin-san and Momiji-san, the red-light district
has become peaceful. Thank you so much.

I can't see Momiji-san anywhere, do you know where she might
be? Where on earth could she have gone...?

Beyond this point, entry to the old red-light district is
forbidden--

I wonder where the missing courtesans were taken... It's
scary to sleep alone, so I'm sleeping with a close friend. I
hope the culprit gets caught soon...

They say that prostitution in bathhouses was common 50 years
ago. But the authorities banned it, limiting it to only the
red-light districts. Even so, there are women who sell
themselves in secret, like the night hawks.

Phew... Even though they're paying, I wish they'd use the
room a bit more cleanly. The customer from earlier even
dirtied the tatami mats, and the smell won't go away even
after cleaning...

Karin-san, shall we go to the ancient brothel, the dwelling
of Aomaru?

Let's go, Momiji-san. If we leave that guy alone, the
courtesans will be in danger again. We must defeat him no
matter what.
--Karin transformed into the guise of Nezumi Komachi!
--Karin and Momiji headed towards the abandoned brothel!
